{"type": "article", "id": 50819, "title": "这个一锤子砸下去才能消停的闹钟，给你｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2018-03-05T23:05:39Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 10665, "name": "品牌设计"}, {"id": 3875, "name": "包装设计"}, {"id": 45217, "name": "Thirst Craft"}, {"id": 9240, "name": "MINI"}, {"id": 48192, "name": "Seo-Yeon Park"}, {"id": 48193, "name": "Yabu Pushelberg"}, {"id": 48194, "name": "Jorge Ros Gisbert"}, {"id": 48195, "name": "Joan Gaspar"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 23, "praise_count": 242, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180305161856WyP70XTe82wlodbc.gif", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s4 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Camping-style Furniture by Yabu Pushelberg </h3><p>针对年轻的千禧一代，万豪国际集团去年在曼哈顿时报广场造了一幢拥有 600 余间客房的新概念旅馆 Moxy Time Square，并邀请设计公司 Yabu Pushelberg 为其设计了一系列野营式家具，以节省酒店的客房空间。</p><p>双层床的设计，每个床位都配有 USB 插槽及插座。房内桌子椅子等家具都可以按照住客的需要摆设，若不需要使用即可折叠收纳挂到墙上。钉在墙上的挂钉还可以用于存放物品，这些挂钩配有定制的衣架，同时在床架上还安装了额外的存储设备。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180305161922jgL0E19Q4e2H7YKU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562207\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180305161933i2jcI7gtzXV8UkCu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.315990\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180305161936fCO54vIWp7badXJS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.330795\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180305161941Nf87jPM2Q0la4bow.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.330795\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180305161948DriPBdF3ablgzQ05.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.330795\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180305161949d5guJGO9WTeaUyDV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.331641\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.dezeen.com/2018/03/03/moxy-times-square-hotel-yabu-pushelberg-rockwell-group-marriott-new-york-us/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dezeen</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Slip-cast Porcelain Tableware by Seo-Yeon Park</h3><p>美国艺术家 Georgia O’Keeffe 的抽象绘画作品中常见的那种颜色和形式，被陶瓷艺术家 Seo-Yeon Park 借用，设计了这套陶瓷餐具。作品以深绿、紫色和淡紫色调为主，也是模仿 O’Keeffe 的名作 The Dark Iris。</p><p>这一系列餐具有着与花瓣非常相似的细腻弯曲的边缘，当把它们嵌套在一起时，这些细长弯曲的边缘聚在一起会给人一朵花的感觉。在 Seo-Yeon Park 看来，色彩的强度和形式的简单性是她设计实践中最为看重的，为了获得强烈的色彩，她尝试将两种或更多重颜料与高纯度的白色陶土混合后，在高温下烧制而成。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180305162047BIRUoA6LaVv8z1Yj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.827991\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180305162047tEPvlOCejo7JcxUm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563034\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180305162048rz1eCmlX2YN9bjHT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562606\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180305162048Xkyqu3OUZS5YHCeI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.dezeen.com/2018/03/03/seo-yeon-park-bases-porcelain-tableware-on-georgia-okeeffe-paintings-ceramics-design/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dezeen</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>MINI Folding Bike</h3><p>MINI 推出了一款新的折叠自行车，意在提供灵活、舒适和时尚的出行方式。它的铝合金车架可以在几秒钟内折叠或迅速展开，使得用户快速轻松地将其装入汽车后备箱，甚至是行李箱中。</p><p>这款车架重量不足 11 公斤，配有加厚皮革鞍座，直径为 50 厘米的车轮，保证提供舒适的骑行体验。此外，铁氟龙涂层链条可防止生锈和顽固污垢，而前后挡泥板则可保护骑行者。座椅本身和车把把手装饰着科涅克白兰地色的皮革，与哑光深灰色的车身以及银色车架搭配。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201803051625532fMhA6HJjwoSPQtL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180305162553polI3rXDBn7498JL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.623472\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180305162553FsG92SLQc6BP3upM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180305162553u6Fhify5UwvNnJ4g.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180305162553moA2hDPEe30FszJf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.361111\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180305162553mLrgbKiyBvlpI3DY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.466993\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180305162554YhMdavy9eWUxGQ53.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.designboom.com/design/new-mini-folding-bike-03-04-2018/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Designboom</a><p><span style=\"color: rgb(54, 54, 54); font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\"><br></span></p><h3><span style=\"color: rgb(54, 54, 54); font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\">Jaima Collection by  Joan Gaspar</span></h3></figcaption></figure></div><p>巴塞罗那设计师 Joan Gaspar 设想出一种新型柔光织物材料制成的灯具，成为西班牙灯具品牌 Marset 的新品系列 Jaima。这个名字来源于北非贝都因人的传统帐篷。</p><p>Jaima 系列提供三种尺寸和四种颜色，其内部裸露的灯源，以便于最大限度地提高光源向下照射的强度，并可以结合两个多功能支架组合使用，用作落地灯或是壁灯，亦可独立悬挂成为吊灯。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180305162650VMXoPquUAv2peRdr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.789731\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180305162650AxJXsl4WHo8vta7j.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.877751\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180305162650q4IsHeZ1MFXPEVm0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.704156\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180305162651OrC3Lt21c9GhvSNB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.292176\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2018030516265190XL3EtRV6fB78TA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.360636\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180305162651fK56cOS2QdRrqexD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.190709\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.marset.com/jaima-bicoca-ganan-premio-design-plus/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Marset</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Loch Lomond Brewery Rebrand by Thirst Craft</h3><p>啤酒品牌 Loch Lomond Brewery 最近开启了品牌重塑，请来了格拉斯哥设计机构 Thirst Craft 操刀品牌设计项目。</p><p>Loch Lomond Brewery 有两个主打系列——传统经典系列与实验工艺品系列，Thirst Craft 提出了以“古代土地的现代视角”这一创意主题，将 Lomond 湖的标志性美景和啤酒包装相结合，用细微的弧线和波浪来描摹当地的山峰和海湾，搭配以定制设计的文字，赋予每款包装生机勃勃的湖泊景观。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180305162731Ek4hMCdnfqAIi1yv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2018030516273180sm56BRErJy3TKZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180305162732ge9mqVhozLSMNu2J.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180305162733P6GzZ59uBLvpYmDA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180305162732mqSfTzEcvloa0sbd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201803051627332muczj1qrGF3nCe6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180305162733EHD2po7b93Yx5GmK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180305162733f25lb4ivNheq9S1n.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.677273\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.creativeboom.com/inspiration/thirst-craft-rebrands-loch-lomond-brewery/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Creativeboom</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Hammer Alarm Clock. by Jorge Ros Gisbert</h3><p>喜欢赖床不起的朋友们也许需要一款这样的闹钟。设计师 Jorge Ros Gisbert 设计了一款“锤子”闹钟，他想要创造一种方式让人们每天醒来感觉充满动力，而不是听到智能手机的闹钟声感到恼怒。</p><p>在听到闹钟声响起后，你必须拿起锤子狠狠砸下去才能关闭声音，厚实的橡胶底座确保了“闹钟的安全”。这可能需要花费点力气，但也是唤醒你的一个好方法，因为你的肌肉已经发动起来了。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201803051629340k5FCK8Vs4dIXZzH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180305162934y48AkM6eEC1dc3YB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180305162820NfWHF5QxJLI7pMEY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.630757\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180305162821d6NYeKqUrQmTAHb2.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.712000\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180305162823JkLzuXUSx1FYgftM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/59254203/LEXON-Hammer-Alarm-Clock\" rel=\"nofollow\">Behance</a></figcaption></figure></div>"}